stim: NO CLIENT WOULD EVER THINK OF ASKING HIM TO DO SUCH THINGS

BUT THE ONLY LOVE I WAS GIVING HIM WAS THE PURE KIND
I ASKED ABOUT THE BATTLE BETWEEN LIFE AND DEATH IN HIS PLAYS
